  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Guideline on Paediatric Investigation Plans, waivers, deferrals and compliance check
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This guidance document from the MHRA provides information on the format and content of paediatric applications in the UK if there is a no-deal Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

